Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}輕輕拂過的風兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:51.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}送來春天的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:55.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}這撥動我心弦的
